            </p>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4" id="Minestle">
                    <a target="_blank" href="https://www.minestle.com/" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                        <div class="verSitio" data-section="section5" data-value="t2">
                            Ver sitio web
                        </div>
                        <div class="template-scroll"></div>
                    </a>
                    <div class="project-description">
                        <h5>Mi Nestlé (Centroamérica)</h5>
                        <p>Sitio con artículos, recetas, promociones y podcast con filtro por país.</p>
                        <span class="badge bg-secondary">Drupal</span>
                        <span class="badge bg-secondary">PHP</span>
                        <span class="badge bg-secondary">CSS3</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4" id="nescafe">
                    <a target="_blank" href="https://www.nescafe.com/cam/" rel="noopener noreferrer">
